(11, 'Bangladesh Agricultural Research Council', 'Natural Resources Management Division', 'Project', 'Carbon sequestration in soils of Bangladesh', 'Soil sample collection and survey will be conducted in all thirty agro-ecological zones of Bangladesh. Different relevant trials and data analysis will be conducted at the experimental fields and respective laboratories of BRRI, BINA and BSMARAU', '', '', '', '01-04-2010', '31-12-2012', '18-04-2010', '', '1.To quantify the present status of carbon in soils in thirty agro-ecological zones of Bangladesh,\r\n2.To determine the effects of different cropping systems and management practices on soil carbon stocks,\r\n3.To evaluate the degree of carbon sequestration using integrated nutrient management,\r\n4.To determine the degree of carbon sequestration in soils using 14C,\r\n5.To establish the relationship among cropping systems and management practices with the soil carbon stock and systems productivity.\r\n', '', '', 'Carbon sequestration, Soil, Agro-ecological zones, Sequestration,  14C, Carbon stock ', 'SPGR', 17500000, 0, 0, '', '', 0, '', '', '', '', ''),
