(74, 'Bangladesh Livestock Research Institute', '', 'Project', 'Development of an effective PPR vaccine from local isolate and its molecular Characterization ID-362', 'The target locations will be at lest 5 outbreaks in each divisions. Besides project will also cover government goat farms and 10 private goat farms (having &gt; 100 goats) when available in the country', '', '', '', '01-07-2011', '30-06-2013', '05-01-2012', '', '1.Development of PPR vaccine seed from local isolate(s).\r\n2.Molecular genetic analysis of field and vaccine isolate(s).\r\n3.Development of serologic and nucleic acid based diagnostic methods to determine the immune response of vaccine seed and for the early diagnosis of PPRV infections and their comparative efficacy.', '', '', 'PPR vaccine, Molecular, ID-362,  Genetic,  Serologic, Infection', 'SPGR', 12995000, 0, 0, '', '', 0, '', '', '', '', ''),
