(98, 'Bangladesh Agricultural Research Institute', 'Agricultural Economics Division', 'Project', 'Study on rural households food security in coastal region of Bangladesh', 'Salkhira, Khulna, Bagherhat, Barguna, Patuakhali, Bhola, Noakhali, Laxmipur and Coxs Bazar', '', '', '', '01-07-2011', '30-06-2014', '', '', '1. To investigate the rural households access to food in terms of food production, household income, asset ownership, and income diversification of farm and non-farm households\r\n2. To estimate the existing rural households food status in the coastal region\r\n3. To explore the coping strategies of coastal people during stress situation, and \r\n4. To suggest some policy guidelines for enhancing coastal peoples living status.  \r\n', '', '', 'households,security, coastal', 'BARC', 750000, 0, 0, '', '', 0, '', '', '', '', ''),
