(1128, 'Bangladesh Forest Research Institute', 'Forestry', 'Project', 'The state of the art of community forestry research in Bangladesh : An annotated bibliographic review.', '', '', 'Evaluation /Impact studies ', 'Completed', '01-06-2000', '31-03-2001', '', '', '1. To identify and collect the major literature on varied dimensions f CF in Bangladesh;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2. to summarise the principal findings and arguments of each of the above literature;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n3. to review, on the basis of the above summary, the current state of research in CF and to trace its principal strengths and weaknesses;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n4. to identify the unexplored or relatively less  explored areas of knowledge and, accordingly, suggest strategies for further investigation;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n5. to consult with the countys leading academics and practitioners in the field of CF in identifying and suggesting future research options;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n6. to present the information in a widely and easily accessible  form, such as book.', '', '', '', 'ARMP', 300000, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'Agroforestry', '', '', '', ''),
