(1123, 'Bangladesh Agricultural University', 'Soil', 'Project', 'Coordinated project for development of Blue Green Algal inoculum for improving soil fertility and reclaiming salinity of soil (BAU component).', '', '', 'Basic', 'Completed', '01-09-1998', '31-08-2001', '01-09-1998', '', 'i)  To identify the salt-tolerant spp. of blue-green algae.\r\nii)  To determine the role of blue-green algae in N-economy of saline rice soils\r\niii)  To select the fast-growing efficient nitrogen fixing salt-tolerant spp. of blue-green algae.\r\niv)  To utilize blue-green algae as a biological means for the reclamation of soil salinity.\r\nv)  To find out the mechanism of reducing soil salinity by blu-green algae.', '', '', '', 'ARMP', 600000, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'Bio-fertilizer', 'Soils', '', '', ''),
