(1121, 'Bangladesh Agricultural Research Institute', 'Soil', 'Project', 'Minimization of soil loss, fertility development and upliftment of farmer''s economy through agrolivestock integration in the hilly region.', '', '', 'Basic', 'Completed', '01-06-1999', '31-05-2001', '01-06-1999', '', 'i)  To estimate soil loss rates from different cultivation method.\r\nii)  To develop an alternative technology which provides erosion control efforts with fertility management though agrolivestock integration.\r\niii)  To find out a relationship between biomass (nitrogen-fixing crop) output and crop production\r\niv)  To create awareness of the dangerous and adverse consequence of soil erosion, deforestation and environment degradation through training and motivating the hilly farmers.\r\nv)  To determine the best and helpful economic components for the upliftment of the hilly farmers through agrolivestock integration.', '', '', '', 'ARMP', 600000, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'Soil Conservation', 'Soils', '', '', ''),
