(1066, 'Bangladesh Agricultural University', 'Soil', 'Project', 'Development of an appropriate technology named &quot;Azobiofer: Azolla as biofertilizer&quot; for Rice Cultivation and improving Soil Fertility.', '', '', 'Adaptive', 'Completed', '01-09-1998', '28-02-2001', '01-07-1998', '', '1) 	To develop a technology for maintenance and production of Azolla inoculum.\r\n\r\n2) 	To develop a suitable technology for using Azolla as biofertilizer for rice production.\r\n\r\n3) 	To improve general soil fertility of rice soils to some extent for sustainable agriculture.', '', '', '', 'ARMP', 400000, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'Bio-fertilizer', 'Soils', '', '', ''),
