(1063, 'Bangladesh Agricultural University', 'Soil', 'Project', 'Studies on Secondary Micronutrients in Soils and Crops of some Major AEZs of Bangladesh', '', '', 'Evaluation /Impact studies ', 'Completed', '01-09-1998', '28-02-2001', '01-10-1998', '', 'i)  To assess the status of the secondary and all micronutrients in soils and crops of major AEZs of Bangladesh .\r\nii)  To delineate the deficient, potential deficient and sufficient area with regards to the status of secondary and micronutrients .\r\niii)  To verify/ update the critical limit of secondary and micronutrients in soils and crops.\r\niv)  To determine the requirement of secondary/micronutrients for sustainable crops yield.', '', '', '', 'ARMP', 648800, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'Fertility Management', 'Soils', '', '', ''),
