(1310, 'Bangabandhu Sheikh Mujibur Rahman Agricultural University', 'Genitic Resources and Seed Division', 'Project', 'Collection of Rice Germplasm from hilly, coastal, haor and other areas of Bangladesh', 'All over Bangladesh', 'High', 'Adaptive', 'Completed', '01-05-2009', '30-04-2011', '', '30-04-2011', 'a. To collect cultivated and wild rice germplasm from unexplored areas especially from hilly, coastal, haor and other areas of Bangladesh.\r\nb. to document the collected rice germplasm for different uses.', 'Orientation training provided to SAAO and Seed Net partners of BRRI in the area where direct collection was not done. In case of direct collection locations were identified checking the previous collection records and filled up passport data and taking photographs of the crops habitats. The germination were sown int he pots/fields for rejuvenation. Only a few samples were characterized morphologically.', 'The exploration and collection were done in the targeted 100 upazilas of 20 districts. The collection missions were able to collect directly from the field and major portion of the collections were done through the DAE personnel and seed net partners of BRRI. In addition, some collected samples were field to germinate which were collected through DAE. It is noted that 371 samples were collected from hilly areas where only 93 accessions ae preserved in BRRI genebank.', 'Rice Germplasm, Hill, Coastal, Haor, Collection of Rice Germplasm', 'Krishi Gobeshona Foundation (KGF)', 1970000, 1346973, 0, 'Report, Booklet', 'Training, Workshop', 474, 'Rice Germplasm', 'Rice', '', '', ''),
