(995, 'Bangladesh Agricultural University', 'AgEng', 'Project', 'Adaptive Research on Solar Dryers for Drying Mango, Pineapple and Fish.', '', '', 'Adaptive', 'Completed', '30-09-1997', '31-08-2000', '01-11-1997', '31-12-2000', 'i) To make a comparative study of the performance of multistacked forced convection solar dryer and solar tunnel dryer.\r\nii) To determine the drying behavior of the fruits in a laboratory dryer.\r\niii) To determine the effects of different pre-treatment on the quality of dried products.\r\niv) To determine sorption isotherms of the fruits.\r\nv) To develop technico-economically viable drying strategies using solar energy.\r\nvi) To adapt and optimise the technico-economic performance of potential dryers suitable for Bangladesh conditions.\r\nvii) To develop a simulation model for drying of mango, pineapple and fish.', '', '', '', 'ARMP', 1837000, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'Agro-Processing', 'Agri Machinery', '', '', ''),
