(974, 'Bangladesh Agricultural University', 'AERS', 'Project', 'An economic study of production, financing and marketing of marine fisheries in Bangladesh.', '', '', 'Evaluation /Impact studies ', 'Completed', '01-08-1999', '31-07-2000', '01-08-1999', '31-12-2000', 'a)	To determine profitability and economic efficiency of production technologies used in marine fisheries.\r\n\r\nb)	To study the nature and extent of variation in the share system of distributing marine earning.\r\n\r\nc)	To determine investment pattern and financing of marine fisheries.\r\n\r\nd)	To study the present status of marine fish marketing aiming to determine marketing costs and margins, and profits of marketing intermediaries both in domestic and export marketing.\r\n\r\ne)	To examine policy implications and suggest the recommendation.', '', '', '', 'ARMP', 675700, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'Finance and Marketing', 'Socio-economics', '', '', ''),
