(938, 'Bangladesh Institute of Nuclear Agriculture', 'Crops', 'Project', 'Study of the cereal research improvement programmes of the National Agricultural Research System in Bangladesh: Rice, wheat and maize.', '', '', 'Evaluation /Impact studies ', 'Completed', '01-07-1999', '31-12-1999', '01-07-1999', '', '1.(a) Review of cereal research programmes (rice wheat and  maize) completed by the scientists of                      relevant research organizations/institutions (from 1989 onward).\r\nb) Determination of degree of success of these completed research programmes.\r\nc) Determination of reasons and/or constraints for shortfall, if any, in achieving the desired objectives.\r\n2.(a) Review the progress of the on-going cereal research programmes being carried out by relevant research organizations/institutions.\r\n(b) Assessment of the on-going cereal research programmes in the light of NARS goal.\r\nc) Assessment of the facilities (infrastructural, manpower and financial) available in carrying out the cereal research programmes.\r\nd) Determination of the stage of progress of the ongoing cereal research programme during the review period.\r\ne) Identification of constraints, if any, experienced by the researchers/ research organizations in conducting the ongoing cereal research programmes.\r\n3 . Determination of the impact of cereal research on the national economy of Bangladesh.  \r\n4. Make appropriate strategic recommendations to the BARC', '', '', '', 'ARMP', 1500000, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'Crop Management', '', '', '', ''),
