(1222, 'Bangladesh Institute of Nuclear Agriculture', 'Plant Breeding Division', 'Project', 'Development of short duration high yielding and high yielding Boro rice varieties through induced mutation', 'Mymensingh, Satkhira, Magura, Barishal, Natore, Rajshahi and Ranjpur', 'High', 'Adaptive', 'On-going', '01-07-2011', '30-06-2014', '01-07-2011', '30-06-2014', '1. To develop short duration (115-120 days) boro rice variety (s) with 6.0-6.5 t/ha yield that can be transplanted after harvest of high yielding mustard/rapeseeds variety\r\n2. To development boro rice variety (s) with high yield potential of 8.0-8.5 t/ha and 155-160 days maturity.\r\n', '', '', 'High yield, Boro rice variety, Short duration of high yield', 'BARC', 1200000, 500000, 0, '', 'Field days', 0, 'Varietal Improvement', 'Rice', '', '', ''),
