(1224, 'Bangladesh Institute of Nuclear Agriculture', 'Biotechnology Division', 'Project', 'Development of salt tolerant rice varieties through induced mutation and market-assisted selection.', 'BINA Mymensingh, Satkhira, Bagerhat, Khulna', 'High', 'Applied', 'On-going', '01-01-2010', '31-12-2012', '', '23-02-2013', 'a.	To screen rice germplasm for salt tolerance at the seedling and reproductive stages using IRRI standard protocol.\r\nb.	To characterize of tested rice genotypes by Molecular (SSR/RAPD) markers.\r\nc.	To map salt tolerant rice genes for QTLs analysis at the seedling and reproductive stages.\r\nd.	To develop salt tolerant rice varieties with acceptable yield using induced mutations and marker-assisted selection (MAS).', '', '', 'Salt tolerant rice varieties, induced mutation, Marker-assisted', 'BARC', 5397170, 4200000, 0, '', '', 0, 'Mutation Breeding and Biotechnology', 'Rice', '', '', ''),
