(1266, 'Bangladesh Rice Research Institute', 'Genetic Resources  and Seed Division', 'Project', 'Strengthening of Rice Breeder Seed Production Maintenance of Nucleus Stock', 'Gazipur Sadar, Comilla Sadar, Rajhahi Sadar, Rangpur Sadar, Habiganj Sadar, Bhanga, Sonagazi, Barisal Sadar and Satkhira Sadar Upazilas', 'High', 'Strengthening  capacity builder', 'On-going', '01-06-2009', '30-11-2012', '01-06-2009', '30-11-2012', 'a.	To strengthen supply of breeder seed to the public and NGO/ private sector clients;\r\nb.	To maintain the quality standard of breeder seed;\r\nc.	To develop exterties on breeder seed as well as seed production technoloty and\r\nd.	To improve technical knowledge on seed production of the concerned clients and ensure its use.\r\n', '1.	Variety maintenance and breeder seed production.\r\n2.	Monitoring of foundation seed production.\r\n3.	Dissemination  of brri developed varieties.\r\n4.	Maintain linkage between BRRI-GO and NGO/private section.\r\n5.	Signing of MOU with seed producing organizations.\r\n6.	Provide technical know how to the seed producers through field visit''\r\n7.	Conduct training on quality seed production with the participation of seed producing public and NGO/private organizations.\r\n8.	Development of documents and aids related to quality seed production.\r\n9.	Conduct workshop seminar etc.\r\n10.	Increase logistic facilities of BRRI to produce more breeder seed.\r\n', '', 'Rice, Rice Breeder seed production, Maintenance of Nucleus stock', 'GoB', 155535000, 140000000, 0, 'Repoet', 'Training', 500, 'Rice Breeder Seed  Production', 'Rice', '', '', ''),
