(1268, 'Bangabandhu Sheikh Mujibur Rahman Agricultural University', 'Irrigation and Water Management Division', 'Project', 'Testing, Validation and Up-scalling to water saving technology in rice production', 'Naogaon and Kishorganj', 'High', 'Adaptive', 'On-going', '01-05-2011', '30-04-2014', '', '30-04-2014', '1. Harvesting and ponding of rainwater for utilization in mitigating drought affected rice.\r\n2. Minimizing conveyance loss and increasing water use efficiency in rice production.\r\n3. Increase irrigated area coverage by adopting water saving technologies and\r\n4. Avoiding repeated priming in STW.\r\n', '', '', 'Water Saving Technology, Rice production', 'Krishi Gobeshona Foundation (KGF)', 3995000, 0, 0, 'Booklet', 'Training, Workshop, Field days', 200, 'Irrigation and Water Management', 'Rice', '', '', ''),
