(1398, 'Bangladesh Agricultural University', 'Dept. of Pathology', 'Project', 'Formulation of rival and synthetic vectors towards delivery of a plasmid DNA vaccine coding for Gonadotrophin releasing Hormone (GnRH)and T-Helper epitopes in rodents. ', 'Overall Country', 'High', 'Applied', 'On-going', '14-05-2012', '30-06-2013', '01-07-2012', '30-06-2013', '1. Develop of DNA vaccine against a reproductive hormone GnRH-1.\r\n2. In vivo fertility assay of the vaccinated animals.\r\n3. Enhance immunoefficacy of a DNA vaccine by means of genetic engineering .\r\n4. Hostologic evaluation of gonadal response followring immunization.\r\n5. Formulation of viral and synthetic vector system for delivery of DNA vaccine in vivo.', '', '', '', 'MoST', 1200000, 0, 0, '', '', 0, '', '', '', '', ''),
