(1424, 'Sylhet Agricultural University', 'Department of Surgery and Obstitries', 'Project', 'Determination of Prevalence and economic impact of ovine footrot in chars and Mymensingh with isolation and molecular characterization of dichelobacter nodosus ', 'Mymensingh', 'High', 'Basic', 'On-going', '01-06-12', '30-06-2013', '01-07-2012', '30-06-2013', '1.To isolate, identify and characterize the D. nodosus bacteria brom different sheep.\r\n2.To compare the prevalence and incidence of footrot in sheep Mymensingh. \r\n3.To identify the infection from non infeeted sheep and carrier taots by PCR technique.\r\n4.To compare the treatment regiment suitable  for the footrot.', '', '', 'Animals, Sheep, Footrot', 'MoST', 2400000, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'D. Nodosus Bacteria and Footrot', 'Animal', '', '', ''),
(1425, 'Sylhet Agricultural University', 'Department of Agricultural Extension Education', 'Project', 'Competence Assessment of the farm volunteer and farmers engaged in One house one farm approach  A case of skill development. ', 'Mymensingh district', 'High', 'Basic', 'On-going', '10-05-2012', '30-06-2013', '01-07-2012', '30-06-2013', '1.To search out the relevant literature on performance of farm volunteer and farmers.\r\n2.To find out the present KSA gap in farm volunteer and farmers\r\n3.To check the awareness level about issue relevant of KSAs on implementing one house and farm approach.\r\n4.To find out the determinates of the competence gap of the respondents.\r\n5.To give policy recommendations for the fulfillment of the capacity gap in the KSA and pointing out gap in effective functioning of farm volunteer and farmers. \r\n', '', '', 'One house and One farm, Aquaculture, Farmers Engaged.', 'MoST', 500000, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'One house and one farm approach', 'Agriculture', '', '', ''),
