(1735, 'Proshika Manobik Unnayan Kendra', '', '', 'Bamboo propagation.', 'Shakipur, Tangail', '', '', '', '', '', '01-04-1999', '31-03-2001', 'A. To demonstrate and describe the easy technique of bamboo propagation through branch cutting to rural poor;   B. To ensure low cost bamboo propagules to farmers that exhibits 100 percent success;                             C. To increase bamboo production and help rural poor in obtaining raw materials for multipurpose uses;        D. To train staffs and the beneficiaries about the bamboo propagation technique to build their technical capabilities;                                     E. To establish a farmer to farmer extension mechanism through the trained farmers in the community;', '', '', '', 'USAID', 300000, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'Forestry', 'Bamboo propagation.', '', '', '');
