(1839, 'Winrock International', '', '', 'Promotion of preservation treatment of bamboo and jute-sticks for enhanced service life.', '', '', '', '', '', '', '01-07-2000', '30-06-2001', 'Familiarise the users of indigenous construction materials like bamboo and jute-stick, with simple preservation treatment technology; Popularise and promote preservative treatment of indigenous construction materials through establishment of demonstration centres in  the  conspicuous trading centres and user location;  Educate the traders and users of bamboo and jute sticks regarding conservation aspects as well as economic advantages of preservation treatment Vis-a-Vis resource constrains in the country;Motivate the traders and users regarding the need for adopting preservative treatment practices for the economic well being of resource users especially of the very low income earning section of the society;Introduce preservative treatment technology in the country side and develop appropriate ways and means to adopt the prescribed methods and equipments by users groups at the grass root level; Contribute to improve housing and wall of betel leaf boroj in the country, conservation of nature and natural resources, ameliorating the natural environment in addition to help technology transfer to real uses;', '', '', '', 'USAID', 300000, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'Forestry', 'Bamboo propagation and preservation.', '', '', ''),
