(1881, 'Bangladesh Agricultural University', 'Department of Fisheries Biology and Genetics', 'Project', 'Study of reproductive biology and genetic variability of bele(Glossogobius giuris) with a view to establishing its induced breeding technique.', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '1) Accumulating information on biology of G.giuris.\r\n2) Analysis of genetic variability of pond, haor and estuarine stocks of G.giuris.\r\n3) Studying morphology and reproductive biology with special emphasis on gonadal maturation through histological observation of individuals from desired genetic make up.\r\n4) Collection and domestication of individuals of desired genetic make up to be used for induced breeding.\r\n5) Conducting trials using various inducing agents to establish a dependable induced breeding technique.\r\n6) Development of rearing technique of larvae for producing stock able sized seed.\r\n7) Arrangement of training for hatchery owners and farmers. ', '', '', '', 'BAS-USDA', 8028000, 0, 0, '', '', 0, '', '', '', '', ''),
