(1921, 'Bangladesh Agricultural University', 'Department of Microbiology and Hygine', 'Project', 'Study on diagnosis and control measures of poultry diseases in selected climatic changes prone delta region of  Bangladesh. ', 'Satkhira sadar upazila, and Santhia - Pabna.', 'High', 'Evaluation /Impact studies ', 'On-going', '01-09-2012', '30-04-2013', '01-09-2012', '30-04-2013', 'a.	To record extent and nature of poultry diseases such as Newcastle diseases (ND) Fowl Cholera (FC), Avian salmonellosis pullorum (SP). Salmonella galinarum (SG), and duck cholera (DC). \r\nb.	Collection of climacal samples followed by isolation and  identification inclusive of characterization of the causal agents of the diseases mentioned above. \r\nc.	Determination of efficacy of currently available bacterins/vaccines at BAV and livestock research institute(LRI) Dhaka, as the case be, in the laboratory and field in order to mitigate impact of climate  changes\r\nd.	Develop maste4r seed to the organism for the preparation of bacterins / vaccines as required in the research area.\r\n', '', '', '', 'Planning Commision of Bangladesh', 1200000, 0, 0, 'Report', '', 0, 'Poultry Diseases', 'Climatic changes', '', '', ''),
