(1955, 'Bangladesh Agricultural University', 'Department of Parasitology', 'Project', 'Studies on the Gastro-intestinal parasites of Buffaloes in some areas of Bangladesh.', '', 'High', 'Applied', '', '01-07-1993', '30-06-1994', '01-07-1993', '30-06-1994', '1) To investigate the types of parasites available in the Gastro-intestinal tract of Buffaloes.\r\n2) To find out the incidence and density of the worms in different ages and sexes.\r\n3) To correlate the parasitic burden in Buffaloes to seasonal changes and agro-climatic conditions.\r\n4) To study the incidence in relation to physiological status of Buffaloes.\r\n5) To suggest effective drug against economic parasites.', 'Methods of Investigation based on:\r\n1) Written materials (Published/manuscript)\r\n2) Field Study.\r\n3) Laboratory/Experimental work.\r\n4) Combination of 1, 2 and 3.', '', 'Gastro-Intestinal, Buffaloes, Parasite', 'BAU-UGC', 97000, 0, 0, 'Report', 'Workshops', 0, '', '', '', '', ''),
