(2374, 'Bangladesh Agricultural University', 'Department of Aquaculture', 'Project', 'Bioremediation of poultry waste and its use to produce microalgae as spirulina platensis and use as feed ingredient in diets for catfish (Clarias batrachus) post larvae', '', 'High', '', 'Completed', '01-07-2010', '30-06-2011', '', '', '1.To grow fly larvae using poultry waste\r\n2.To analyze the physico-chemical properties of poultry waste\r\n3.To couture microalgae as spirulina, spirulina platensis in supernatant of digested poultry waste;\r\n4.To determine the nutritional values of spirulina and\r\n5.To study the growth performance and nutritional values of catfish, Clarias batrachus post-larvae using feed prepared with spirulina and fish meal.\r\n', '', '', 'Poultry, Catfish', 'MOSICT', 2938000, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'Biological Science', 'Fishes', '', '', ''),
(2372, 'Bangladesh Agricultural University', 'Department of Aquaculture, BAU', 'Project', 'Maximum utilization of artificial feed used in aquaculture through integration.', '', 'High', 'Applied', 'Completed', '01-07-2010', '30-06-2011', '01-07-2010', '30-06-2011', '1.	To observe the growth performance of tilapia with artificial feed in recirculatory system\r\n2.	To evaluate the growth performance of vegetables in the integrated recirculatory system\r\n3.	To evaluate the utilization of nitrogen and phosphorus in feed by fish and vegetables.\r\n4.	To evaluated the performance of sediment as fertilizer for crop production\r\n5.	To evaluate the water quality parameters in the system during the study period.\r\n', 'Water quality parameter (NH4, N02, N03, P04 total phosphorus) will bne measured fortnightly following the method used  in standard methods 2000 with the help of Hach kit; alkalinity will be measured with the help of a portable alkalinity meter; DO and pH will be recorded with the help of a portable DO meter and Portable pH meter respectively.\r\nafter several weeks sediment will be collected and mixed with the  soil at three different ratios to prepare the media for the crop and vegetable production in pots. ', '', '', 'MOSICT', 1200000, 0, 0, 'Report', '', 0, '', '', '', '', ''),
