(2367, 'Bangladesh Agricultural University', 'Department of Farm Power and Machinery', 'Project', 'Design, Development and performance studies of a power tiller mounted Hydraulic sprayer.', 'Department of Farm Power and Machinery, BAU, Mymensingh-2202', 'High', 'Applied', '', '01-01-2010', '31-12-2010', '', '', 'a.	Design and development of a power tiller mounted sprayer in the workshop of the department of farm power and machinery.\r\n1.	Design of power transmission system.\r\n2.	election of appropriate pump unit tank size and frame for supporting pump unit tank,\r\n3.	Design of nozzle, nozzle holder and attachment system with the boom and installation.\r\nb.	Performance studies of the sprayer.\r\n1.	To measure flow rate, swath at various spray angle, height of spraying and nozzle orientation with the boom.\r\n2.	Spray deposit distribution on a patternator and corresponding drift at laboratory and field operations under different operating conditions.\r\n3.	Economics of hydraulic type boom sprayer over the hand held sprayer.\r\n', '', '', 'Power tiller, Farm machinery, Sprayer', 'AU-UGC', 40000, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'Design, Development and performance', 'Powertiller', '', '', '');
