(2556, 'Bangladesh Agricultural University', 'Department of Poultry Science', 'Project', 'Effect of using oil extracted Koroch (Pongania pinnate) seedcake in the diet broiler and meat type duck.', 'BAU poultry farm, My-2202', 'High', 'Applied', 'On-going', '01-01-2013', '31-12-2014', '01-01-2013', '31-12-2014', '1.	To develop an easy and cost effective method of using de-oiled Koroch seed cake as a feed ingredient in broilers and ducks.\r\n2.	To find out suitable processing methods for oil extracted Koroch cake for the diet of broiler and ducks.\r\n3.	To investigate the effect of different levels of oil extracted Koroch cake on growth, meat yield and survivability of broilers and ducks. \r\n', '', '', 'Animals, Broiler, Diseases, Poultry', 'BAU', 300000, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'Diseases', 'Poultry', '', '', ''),
