(2630, 'Bangladesh Agricultural University', 'Department of Graduate Training Institute', 'Project', 'Performance Evaluation of Public University Teachers for Quality Improvement in Higher Education.', 'BAU, Mymensingh-2202', 'High', 'Applied', 'Completed', '01-07-2007', '30-06-2008', '01-07-2007', '30-06-2008', '1.	Assessment of performance of university teachers.\r\n2.	Determination of personal attributes of respondent teachers and identification of dominant indicator attribute of performance in teaching.\r\n3.	Identification of problems limiting the performance of teaching and the ways to solve these problems.\r\n4.	Formulate recommendations to improve performance of teachers to achieve quality higher education.\r\n', 'Teachers of all public university of Bangladesh will constitute the population for this study. Fifty percent of the total university will be selected at random and ten percent samples from the teachers of these universities will be drawn following stratified random sampling technique. A combination of qualitative and quantitative research methods will be used to fulfill the objective so the study. A framework for measuring performance will be developed and data related to performance along with personal attribute will be developed through literature study and consulting with relevant expert and beneficiaries. Appropriate statistical tools will be employed to find out the indicating attributes of the teachers towards better performance. \r\nCalendar or Work: Literature review and sampling, development of performance measurement tools, data collection from different universities, data processing and analysis, report writing and submission of final report.\r\n', '\r\n', 'Education, Quality, Public Univeristy, Study quality', 'University Grants Commission of Bangladesh', 68400, 0, 0, 'Report', '', 0, 'Quality', 'Education', '', '', ''),
