(2666, 'Bangladesh Agricultural University', 'Department of Crop Botany', 'Project', 'Natural nitrification inhibition by sorghum plants-a novel genetic strategy can boost nitrogen use efficiency in rice production. ', '', 'High', 'Applied', 'Completed', '', '', '', '', '1.	To identify the high and low genetic stock for BNI capacity from a wide range of sorghum germplasms. \r\n2.	Physiological studies on the mechanisms of BNI-compounds release; model of action of BNI release from roots. \r\n3.	To evaluate the ability and stability of the nitrification inhibitory compounds in the soil. \r\n4.	To evaluate the effect of BNI-compounds released from sorghum roots in increasing NUE by rice plants. \r\n5.	Finally this trait con be introduced to the rice plant through breeding or biotechnological approach.\r\n6.	To study the effect of BNI-compounds on the physiological parameters of rice plants and to study their effect on the efficiency of C and N assimilation in plants. \r\n', '', '', 'Rice, Production, boost nitrogen', 'MOSICT', 0, 0, 0, 'Report', '', 0, 'Production', 'Rice', '', '', ''),
(2667, 'Bangladesh Agricultural University', 'Department of Horticulture', 'Project', 'Development of a package of technology for enhancing yield, quality and shelf life of mango.', '', 'High', 'Applied', 'Completed', '', '', '', '', '1.	To find out the best management practices for quality mango production with higher yield.\r\n2.	To determine the effective measures for the management of diseases and insects.\r\n3.	To extend the shelf life and maintain quality of fruits through post harvest treatments; and finally\r\n4.	To develop a package of technology for enhancing the yield, quality and shelf life of mango. \r\n', 'a.	Title: Development of a package of technology for enhancing yield, quality and shelf life of mango.\r\nb.	Experiment: effect of fertilizer dose and time of application on flowering, fruit setting, fruit quality and yield of mango.\r\nc.	Treatment: Factor A (Fertilizer dose), Factor B (time of application).\r\n', '', 'Mango, Storage, Fruit, enhancing the yield.', 'MOSICT', 0, 0, 0, 'Report', '', 0, 'Stotrage', 'Fruit', '', '', ''),
