(2418, 'Bangladesh Agricultural University', 'Department of Agricultural Finance', 'Project', 'An investigation into the opverty alleviation programme of BKB in a selected area of Netrokona district', '', 'High', 'Applied', 'Completed', '01-07-1995', '30-06-1996', '', '', 'a.To assess the socioeconomic characteristics of the beneficiaries under the programme in the study area.\r\nb.To overview the economic activities and loan sanction under micro credit programme by the BKB.\r\nc.To investigate into the actual utilization and repayment of credit received by the borrowers under the programme in the study area.\r\nd.To assess the effects of micro credit programme in alleviating rural poverty in the study villages.\r\ne.To draw some guidelines for future improvement of the programme adopted by the BKB.\r\n', '', '', '', 'Bangaldesh Krishi Bank (BKB)', 0, 0, 0, '', '', 0, '', '', '', '', ''),
