(2976, 'Bangladesh Agricultural University', 'Department of Fisheries Management', 'Project', 'A study of the causes of noxious and toxic phytoplankton blooms in ponds', 'Department of Fisheries Management, BAU', 'High', 'Applied', 'Completed', '01-01-2001', '31-12-2003', '01-01-2001', '31-12-2003', '1) Identification and isolation of different species of Cyanobacteria, blue-green algae.\r\n2) Examination of the occurrence, abundance and seasonal dynamics of different species of cyanobacteria\r\n3) Determination of the effects of environmental factors such as temperature, light, nutrients etc. both in the field and laboratory cultures that triggers the initiation of noxious and toxic algal blooms.\r\n4) Determination of the possible hazards caused by the blooms of freshwater noxious and toxic algae\r\n5) Preliminary laboratory test of some chemicals as killing agents of noxious algae and their effects on fish.', '1) Experimental ponds\r\n2) Collection, identification, isolation and culture of algae\r\n3) Investigation of the effects of environmental factors on the initiation of noxious algal blooms\r\n4) Toxicity test\r\n5) Determination of possible hazards\r\n', '', '', 'BAURES', 383940, 0, 0, 'Report', '', 0, 'Fish production', 'Phytoplankton', '', '', ''),
