(2994, 'Bangladesh Agricultural University', 'Department of  Plant Pathology', 'Project', 'Bio-Control of Post-harvest Diseases of Potato', 'Department of  Plant Pathology, BAU', 'High', 'Applied', 'Completed', '01-07-2007', '30-06-2009', '01-07-2007', '30-06-2009', '1.	To survey the prevalence of post-harvest potato diseases in the market and in the storage.\r\n2.	To estimate the loss incurred due to post-harvest potato diseases in the market and the storage.\r\n3.	To isolate and identify the pathogens from infected tubers\r\n4.	To observed the effect of some plant extracts and bio-agents against post-harvest potato diseases.\r\n', 'The main Methodology of the research Project have been given below: \r\na.	Material:\r\nb.	Design of Experiments:\r\nc.	Procedure to be followed in achieving stated objectives:\r\nd.	Data collection\r\ne.	Data analysis.', '', '', 'BAU', 200000, 0, 0, 'Report', '', 0, '', '', '', '', ''),
