(3090, 'Bangladesh Agricultural University', 'Department of Food Technology and Rural Industries (FT&amp;RI)', 'Project', 'Production of protein concentrate3 from rice bran and its food applications.', '', 'High', 'Applied', 'Completed', '01-10-2000', '30-09-2003', '01-10-2000', '30-09-2003', '1.	Analysis of commercially available rice bran for its chemical constituents, nutritional constituents and microbial status.\r\n2.	Preparation of protein concentrate from rice bran by non-alkaline aqueous extraction process and analysis of the prepared protein concentrate for its chemical composition and nutritional constituents.\r\n3.	Examination of functional properties of protein concentrate such as dough rheological properties, oil absorption, water holding capacity, solubility and others.\r\n4.	Sensory evaluation of the various high-protein foods products prepared by incorporating protein concentrate.\r\n5.	Studies on storage stability of dried rice bran protein concentrate shall be carried out on the basis of various analytical tests. \r\n', 'The main Methodology of the research Project have been given below: \r\na.	Material:\r\nb.	Design of Experiments:\r\nc.	Procedure to be followed in achieving stated objectives:\r\nd.	Data collection\r\ne.	Data analysis.\r\n', '', 'Rice, Production, Protein', 'BAURES', 225000, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'Production', 'Rice', '', '', ''),
