(3400, 'Bangladesh Agricultural University', 'Department of Aquaculture', 'Project', 'Investigation into the Disease condition of cultured Koi Anabas testudineus in Mymensingh and its control.\r\n', 'Inland water bodies of Gazipur, Tangail, Sherpur, Jamalpur, Netrokona, Kishorganj and Mymensingh districts.', 'High', 'Applied', 'Completed', '01-07-2009', '30-06-2011', '01-07-2009', '30-06-2011', '1) Exploration of disease condition of Koi.\r\n2) Detection of the potential pathogen causing disease in Koi by their identification and characterization.\r\n3) Understanding the ecology of the potential pathogen in culture environment of Koi.\r\n4) Detection of the diseases by histopathological investigation.\r\n5) Achievement of the specific control measure of disease of Koi fish.\r\n6) Motivating the farmers for specific treatment of Koi and thus increasing its production.\r\n7) Establishment of rapid immuno-diagnostic technique for diagnosis of the most common disease of Koi.\r\n8) Steps towards vaccination against the specific disease of the Koi fish.  ', 'A. Area, Duration and Sample\r\nB. Disease investigation\r\n1. Clinical record\r\n2. Bacteriological work\r\n3. Detection by PCR\r\n4. Disease control\r\n5. Study with the pathogen\r\nC. Immunodiagnosis\r\nD. Vaccination', 'The study is planned to be undertaken with the objectives of identifying the causative bacteria of the disease condition of the indigenous Koi Anabas testudineus, to know the infection pattern of the pathogen, to control the disease in an economically profitable measure and to step towards the immunodiagnostic measures with the aim of successful vaccination against the disease.', 'Anabas testudineus, immunodiagnostic, Disease investigation, Detection by PCR', 'BAURES', 240000, 0, 0, 'Report', '', 0, 'Disease management', 'Fish (Koi)', '', '', ''),
