(3645, 'Bangladesh Agricultural University', 'Department of Parasitology', 'Project', 'Status of Gid disease in calves', 'Department of Parasitology, BAU', 'High', 'Applied', 'Completed', '', '', '', '', '1) To study the incidence of Gid disease in calves.\r\n2) To record the seasonal variations of the disease\r\n3) T ascertain the localization of the cyst in the brain of calves.\r\n4) To suggest effective control.', 'Calves randomly will be examined to record the age, sex, breed and health status and heads will be collected from the slaughter houses and markets of the main localities of Mymensingh district. The heads will be skinned off and thoroughly dissected using a probe and a pair of forceps. The care will be taken so that the cyst may not rupture in positive cases. During dissection, the brain tissue will be flushed with normal saline. The detection of tiny cyst will be aided by a magnifying glass. The anatomical location of the cyst in the brain will be recorded. The number of cysts in the brain and their diameters will also be noted.', '', 'Gid disease of calves, cyst in the brain of calves', 'BAU-UGC', 0, 0, 0, 'Report', '', 0, 'Animal disease management', 'Gid disease of calves', '', '', ''),
