(66, 'Mixed culture of Thai Pangus with other carps.', 'A. Thai Pangas culture is limited within some Govt. farms, some private owned fisheries sector and within a few NGOs only. This culture is not well disseminated throughout the country and there are  some areas in Bangladesh where the village people even did not hear the name of Thai Pangas;                                          B. The mono culture of Thai Pangas and mixed culture with other carps have been proved environmentally viable, economically benefited, socially accepted and scientifically approved. But due to the lackings of proper extension services by the Govt. and other institutions, the pangas culture in pond has not yet been expanded to the farmers;', 'Proshika Manobik Unnayan Kendra', 'Fisheries', 'Mixed carp culture with Thai Pangus.', 'Dr. Md. Zahid Hossain', 'Co-ordinator', '1999-07-01', '2001-06-30', 'Kuliarchar. Kishoreganj', '400000', 'USAID'),
